Text: Mcluv, I really mean this.  You made my summer!!!  Thanks a ton.
Thanks again, McLuv, for all of your "help" this tour!

Thanks for your uploads this year McLuv. I really truly appreciate it. I'm assuming we won't get any more live material until next year sometime, perhaps summer. I think Gordon is doing some solo/non-Phish stuff in March, which I'm guessing means they won't be doing a spring/late winter 2012 tour.
